<node id="World Athletics Federation">
  <data key="d0">World Athletics Federation</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">国际田联（World Athletics Federation）是负责监督世界田径锦标赛和记录认证的管理机构。作为全球田径运动的最高管理机构，国际田联负责组织和管理各种国际田径比赛，包括但不限于世界田径锦标赛。该组织还负责认证和维护田径项目中的各项纪录，确保其公正性和准确性。通过这些努力，国际田联在推动全球田径运动的发展和普及方面发挥着至关重要的作用。&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.</data>
